	A fantastic wooden incense tower in the shape of a lighthouse.&nbsp; Perfect for burning your chosen incense sticks in to allow your room to fill with the aroma as the smoke filters through the carved wooden shapes in the wooden tower.&nbsp; Also ideal for catching the ash from the burnt incense stick.&nbsp; Simply light the tip of your incense stick, blow the flame out and place in one of the three specially designed holes in the base then sit back and enjoy indulgent relaxation with beautiful aroma.&nbsp; The base also has a metal well for burning cones or dhoop. We also have available a large range of incense sticks so you can choose your favourite aroma or why not try something new!&nbsp; This quality wooden incense tower stands approximately 380mm tall.</p>
